                        <b>How to edit the file?</b>
                        <p>To edit the settings of your file, first, access the file management section of the platform. Within the settings menu, you'll find various options for customizing your file's settings. These options may include file name, description, privacy settings, sharing permissions, and more. Simply select the setting you wish to modify, make your changes, and save your updates.</p>

